codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.managers

Class PowerOrbManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.managers.PowerOrbManager

  • public class PowerOrbManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for managing active PowerOrbs around the player. Insert orbs that get detected and get the active orb with the PowerOrbType.getPriority() highest priority}.

      • get

        public PowerOrb get()
        Get the active orb with the highest priority. Priority is based on the value defined in PowerOrbType.getPriority() and the returned orb is guaranteed to have been active at least 100ms ago.
        Returns:
        Highest priority orb or null if none is around
